-Nate

fields.title: SiGe JJ 337 - Al Shield

SiGe JJ project - initial measurements to test that devices are working.
2D plots: dVdI, Vdc, Gate Leakage as function of Idc and Vg. 
Requires: SR860, CS580, Keithley 2450, 2 voltage amplifiers, 1 current amplifier, DMM, QDAC-II
